data.description: Beautiful, private estate off of Beerman Creek Road near Seaside. 7 acres total, treed entrance, fenced pastures, 3832 sq. ft. home features vaulted wood beam ceilings, walls of windows, inviting living room with wood burning fireplace, sizable kitchen/nook, large decks, sauna, 3 bay shop/garage with large bonus/party room. Country living close to town!
